{"tid":912240,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大家肯放過馬紀筠未？","createTime":"2018-11-22T13:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T06:14:06.000Z","uid":143288,"like":8,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"e6fc3dad7997aa86655cf0c70c92245c0cc18c0d","tid":912240,"uid":143288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:31:49.000Z","msg":"你班仆街咁耐都唔肯放過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人"},{"pid":"157bd1549c8070ac1b98ea8675986d375d8e0889","tid":912240,"uid":80107,"like":116,"dislike":1,"score":115,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:33:39.000Z","msg":"咪係 本身已經唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6ce2bd3884e9773b653ac6b7a781e6fb73d252","tid":912240,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a7fd6305b3c2980e7841ec68b975adbfb16bca","tid":912240,"uid":172507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"重溫下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee4ac6680955f81129cd49f5c97fa2ede7f8c0f","tid":912240,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:37:15.000Z","msg":"又回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626d38d0280f6069c6af9aefe2a9d518366c05c0","tid":912240,"uid":143288,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:43:13.000Z","msg":"片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.buzzav.com/video/900\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzav.com%2Fvideo%2F900&d=mrqfO2acVYv3V1DatE9AOcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=ba5cbddf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.buzzav.com/video/900</a>"},{"pid":"a56ef1a66dc964f83237e650752b567c5a006981","tid":912240,"uid":143288,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:43:49.000Z","msg":"我給馬紀筠的情書 <br />\n<br />\n如果一個人有70歲命的話，即係25,567日，原來我同妳己經一起經歷左17.7%（4,525日）。 <br />\n<br />\n今日係2016年2月14日情人節，除左向妳表達我對妳既愛意同時，還希望可以跟妳回顧我們的過去。<br />\n<br />\n我同妳相遇既第一日係2003年9月26日 <br />\n<br />\nCSKMS 1E 班房 紅十會第一次既聚會，雖然透過輪流介紹認知對方名稱，鄧兆匡・馬紀筠，彼此都留下好淡既印像，雖然交談不多，但早而對妳有好感。 <br />\n<br />\n從前妳一個眼神，讓我由一個硬石頭，軟化起來 <br />\n<br />\n直到今日12年多既日子，妳給予我色彩，多資多采既生活，感激妳！ <br />\n<br />\n感激遇見妳！ <br />\n<br />\n愛係一種感覺，係緣份把我們第三次再次拉在一起。 <br />\n<br />\n我記得對上兩次雖然分開了，但彼此都感受到大家都愛大家 <br />\n<br />\n愛係來自信任，2009年3月7日，剛跟妳第2次分開後，一次朋友既生日Party，妳飲醉左，因為妳信我，妳同我去左酒店，最終什麼事都無發生。 <br />\n<br />\n愛而非佔有，我記得2011年3月14日我到妳家樓下公園，表達了愛意，但因為唔懂得去愛所以最終無起埋一齊 <br />\n<br />\n我知道原來我對妳既愛一開始已經跟男女朋友無關，我對馬紀筠既愛 不受地方，關係，時間限制，只要有馬紀筠就有鄧兆匡既愛 <br />\n<br />\n妳對我既愛 <br />\n<br />\n如果用信任對方＝愛，妳對我既愛係世上無人能及，結婚晢詞常提及：從今以後無論環境順逆，疾病健康，我都會愛謢你。 <br />\n<br />\n跟妳一起拍拖4年多，我經歷過無數上述高低起跌，妳都無離棄我多謝妳。"},{"pid":"e789d23839352b988143e65048bc64c213ffea24","tid":912240,"uid":73853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:11:25.000Z","msg":"唔好推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d9f6839d11e3d49ab3481324ca9b274ad707b3","tid":912240,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:13:24.000Z","msg":"其實只係一班買唔起樓的窮酸肥毒宅<br />\n眼紅人地賣樓搵到錢"},{"pid":"f7d5be555f3a721ede663a52b658cb6482a26db0","tid":912240,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:14:14.000Z","msg":"Who?"},{"pid":"1c8bca1dc3af41aa7521748051a6125fdbff652b","tid":912240,"uid":88309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"681ff8ae9ddd4e42178d292d4ed74e04349ff53f","tid":912240,"uid":93649,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:26:24.000Z","msg":"其實佢真係好錫肥仔男朋友<br />\n吹又吹得落力<br />\n明知肥仔軟皮蛇都係床上交足戲<br />\n係好女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ef40b1ee22b2792f952ac3e9dd22b59c2ca21f","tid":912240,"uid":146435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:28:12.000Z","msg":"記得有張gif圖好正 個肥仔射完精好似就死咁"},{"pid":"786a57dc9491ec7fea78e53fd8fea807705cf703","tid":912240,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:29:20.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"8b49553b46ead13461ea53164f5484ef1d1c5671","tid":912240,"uid":100741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:32:02.000Z","msg":"之前夜晚係元朗見過佢，本身認唔到，見到肥仔先知係佢，無化妝個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830be3944546c8cd51813f586699a2d582f1bd46","tid":912240,"uid":207462,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:03:24.000Z","msg":"仲記得有條片唔知點解肥仔頭上面係咁出啲心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b48298ec9d11e99fdd3d38dc91a8e0ad80ff4f8","tid":912240,"uid":131690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"830be3944546c8cd51813f586699a2d582f1bd46","tid":912240,"uid":207462,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:03:24.000Z","msg":"仲記得有條片唔知點解肥仔頭上面係咁出啲心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:14:53.000Z","msg":"應該出煙先岩"},{"pid":"a18da1b63074dc48eeb35218d29cfd281aeea8f4","tid":912240,"uid":4168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T16:34:16.000Z","msg":"一炮成名<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7376517c2061c344f7da8cd51d1715610b37743d","tid":912240,"uid":63253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T16:38:22.000Z","msg":"馬紀筠影迷會（4 )<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/283924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://li